	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hello,<br />I was wondering if it is possible to use more than one EPROM (namely 27c322) with the use of a 74LS139. If it is, how would it be connected? Pin 1 goes to /OE obviously but would I need to connect Pin 2 and 3 to A21/A22 or somewhere else? Help is appreciated, if someone knows how to do this.<br />I'm planning to put the BadApple Demo (which is 8MB btw) on a cart just to test how it works.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


