		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: [MD/Gen] Multi EPROMs</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />You should probably ask on a forum that knows more about the megadrive... my best guess is that you'll hook up 68000.A22 to 74139.A, 68000.A23 to 74139.B, 68000./AS to 74139./G, and 74139./Y0 and /Y1 to the two ROM's /CE pins.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


